NK041(di)051:1: // 'phags pa bkra shis brtsegs pa'i mdo bzhugs so //
NK041(di)051:3: +aar+ya mang+ga la k+au ta n+aa ma ma h+aa y+aa na s+au tra /
NK041(di)051:5: 'phags pa bkra shis brtsegs pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo /
NK041(di)051:6: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)051:7: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
NK041(di)051:8: bcom ldan 'das ri bo mchog gi gnas /
NK041(di)051:9: bkra shis brtsegs pa'i pho brang /
NK041(di)051:11: rdo rje brtsegs pa'i gur khang /
NK041(di)051:13: ge sar pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs te /
NK041(di)051:14: bkra shis pa'i 'khor mang po dang ldan pa /
NK041(di)051:15: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po stong rtsa brgyad kyis bskor ba ni /
NK041(di)051:17: byang chub sems dpa' bkra shis mchog dang /
NK041(di)051:18: byang chub sems dpa' bkra shis sdud dang /
NK041(di)051:19: byang chub sems dpa' bkra shis rgyan dang /
NK041(di)051:20: byang chub sems dpa' bkra shis kun tu gzigs dang /
NK041(di)051:21: byang chub sems dpa' bkra shis yongs su khyab pa dang /
NK041(di)051:22: bkra shis byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK041(di)051:23: bkra shis byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po dang /
NK041(di)051:24: bkra shis byang chub sems dpa' rlung gi snying po dang /
NK041(di)051:25: bkra shis byang chub sems dpa' me'i snying po dang /
NK041(di)051:26: bkra shis byang chub sems dpa' chu'i snying po dang /
NK041(di)051:27: bkra shis byang chub sems dpa' rdo'i snying po dang /
NK041(di)051:28: bkra shis byang chub sems dpa' rin po che'i snying po dang /
NK041(di)051:29: bkra shis byang chub sems dpa' bkod pa mtha' yas dang /
NK041(di)051:30: de bzhin du rnam par gzigs dang /
NK041(di)051:35: bkra shis dam pa'i tog can dang /
NK041(di)051:36: bkra shis mthu stobs dang ldan pa lag na rdo rje dang /
NK041(di)051:37: bkra shis mkhyen pa dang ldan pa 'jam dpal dang /
NK041(di)051:38: bkra shis thugs rje dang ldan pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
NK041(di)051:39: sh+aa ri'i bu dang rab 'byor la sogs pa'i bkra shis pa'i 'khor stong rtsa brgyad dang /
NK041(di)051:40: gzhan yang lha dang klu dang /
NK041(di)051:42: dri za dang grul bum dang /
NK041(di)051:43: mi dang mi ma yin pa'i tshogs rab tu mang po dang thabs gcig tu bzhugs te /
NK041(di)051:44: de'i tshe de'i dus na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa stan las langs te /
NK041(di)051:45: bcom ldan 'das la bskor ba mang du mdzad de /
NK041(di)051:46: pus mo g.yas pa'i lha nga sa la btsugs te /
NK041(di)051:47: bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK041(di)051:48: bcom ldan 'das bkra shis dang ldan pa'i 'khor mang
NK041(di)051:49: po bzhugs pa'i skabs 'dir thog mar bkra shis shing
NK041(di)051:50: dge ba / bar du bkra shis shing dge ba /
NK041(di)051:51: tha mar bkra shis shing dge ba /
NK041(di)051:52: bkra mi shis pa thams cad zhi bar byed pa /
NK041(di)051:53: bkra shis pa thams cad yongs su 'du bar byed pa /
NK041(di)051:54: nyes skyon sel ba legs pa'i yon tan thams cad yongs su 'du bar byed pa /
NK041(di)051:55: dpal dang skal pa bzang por byed pa'i mdo zhig bstan du gsol zhes zhus pa dang /
NK041(di)051:56: bcom ldan 'das kyis zhal 'dzum pa mdzad nas 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NK041(di)051:57: 'jam dpal gzhan yang bkra shis dang ldan pa'i 'khor rnams nyon cig /
NK041(di)051:58: ngas sngon bram ze'i lus kyis mi mjed kyi 'jig
NK041(di)051:59: rten gyi khams 'dir tshe lo stong thub pa'i tshe
NK041(di)051:60: / yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bkra shis
NK041(di)051:61: thams cad 'byung ba'i dpal gzi brjid ces bya ba
NK041(di)051:62: la bkra shis brtsegs pa zhes bya ba theg pa
NK041(di)051:63: / chen po'i mdo / yon tan stong ldan zhes bya ba'i chos kyi rnam grangs 'di thos te /
NK041(di)051:64: bzung zhing bcangs te bklags shing bshad de /
NK041(di)051:65: 'jig rten gyi khams 'di la legs nyes kyi dbang
NK041(di)051:66: gis bkra mi shis pa'i rtags mang du byung ste
NK041(di)051:69: lo zla mi shis pa la sogs pa dang /
NK041(di)051:76: rta phyugs bsrel nyes pa dang /
NK041(di)051:82: dur gdab nyes pa la sogs te bkra mi shis pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar byed pa /
NK041(di)051:83: bkra shis pa thams cad rab tu 'du bar byed pa /
NK041(di)051:84: nyes skyon thams cad rab tu sel ba /
NK041(di)051:85: legs pa'i yon tan thams cad yongs su 'du bar byed pa /
NK041(di)051:86: dpal dang skal pa bzang por gyur pa /
NK041(di)051:87: thog mtha' bar du dge ba /
NK041(di)051:88: bsod nams thams cad yongs su sdud pa /
NK041(di)051:89: bkra shis kyi tshogs thams cad 'char zhing shes pa /
NK041(di)051:90: sdig sgrib thams cad med par 'phags pa /
NK041(di)051:91: bkra shis brtsegs pa chen po'i mdo ngas khyod la bstan gyis /
NK041(di)051:92: 'di thos sam brtsams shing brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK041(di)051:93: bkra mi shis pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar byed pa /
NK041(di)051:97: ltas ngan pa thams cad zlog par byed pa'i mdo sde sems can thams cad la phan pa dang /
NK041(di)051:98: sman pa dang bde ba'i phyir khyod la ngas bstan gyis /
NK041(di)051:99: rab tu nyon la yid la chongs shig ces bka' stsal to //
NK041(di)051:100: de la 'jal dpal gyis legs so legs so //
NK041(di)051:101: bcom ldan 'das sems can thams cad kyi bkra mi
NK041(di)051:102: shis pa thams cad zlog par byed pa'i don du
NK041(di)051:103: / bkra shis brtsegs pa zhes bya ba'i mdo sde
NK041(di)051:104: yon tan bkod pa'i rgyal po chos kyi phung po
NK041(di)051:105: de bdag cag rnams la bshad du gsol zhes zhus
NK041(di)051:106: / pa dang / bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK041(di)051:107: 'jam dpal gzhan yang bkra shis dang ldan pa'i 'khor dag skye 'gro mtha' dag la las dang /
NK041(di)051:108: bsod nams 'phel shugs kyis bkra shis pa dang bkra mi shis pa gnyis su byung ste /
NK041(di)051:109: sems can gyi nang nas kyang mi'i rigs su gyur pa la /
NK041(di)051:110: bkra mi shis pa'i rtags ni klag nyes pa dang /
NK041(di)051:114: skyes ma thag tu 'chi ba dang /
NK041(di)051:118: sho re dwa sgal zhar sgur dang /
NK041(di)051:119: gzi mig drug lag gdong sme can /
NK041(di)051:120: lba ba sha lhag sha mtshan dang /
NK041(di)051:121: gtsug ngan pa dang sha 'dzer can /
NK041(di)051:122: yan lag chad lhag byung ba rnams bkra mi shis pa'i skyon yin te /
NK041(di)051:123: de bzhin phyugs dang sgo khyi dang zhing khang nor rdzas kun la yang /
NK041(di)051:124: bkra mi shis pa'i skyon mang du byung ste /
NK041(di)051:125: de'i mtshan ma ngan pa dang /
NK041(di)051:126: rtags sogs bkra mi shis pa kun /
NK041(di)051:127: thams cad zlog cing bsgyur ba ste /
NK041(di)051:128: nyes skyon med par bya ba'i phyir bkra shis don gyi lha lnga la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)051:129: bkra shis mchog gi lha phyogs skyong mgon po rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)051:130: bkra shis par byed pa'i sngags brjod par bya'o //
NK041(di)051:131: s+y+aad ya the ngan b+hi dz+ny+aa ye b+hi dz+ny+aa ye /
NK041(di)051:132: ug ge ug gi swasti kra pa ti /
NK041(di)051:133: u mu kh+hi pra swa ra dwa /
NK041(di)051:134: swasti swasti brum brum brum pra ha k+she /
NK041(di)051:136: gu ra ne gu ra ne /
NK041(di)051:138: mu ra ke mu ra ke /
NK041(di)051:139: a ma ti gu ra na ya /
NK041(di)051:143: tsu ra na tsu ra na /
NK041(di)051:145: zhes tshig 'di rab tu brjod do //
NK041(di)051:146: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK041(di)051:147: phyag 'tshal skyabs gsol shis gyur cig /
NK041(di)051:148: phyi nang gsang ba'i bkra shis rnams //
NK041(di)051:150: phyi ru bkra shis nam mkha' dag pa'i mkha' //
NK041(di)051:151: nang du bkra shis sems nyid dag pa'i klong //
NK041(di)051:152: gsang ba'i bkra shis chos nyid dag pa'i dbyings //
NK041(di)051:153: mkha' klong dbyings gsum bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:154: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:155: gnam la bkra shis nyi zla gnyis //
NK041(di)051:156: gza' skar mang po'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NK041(di)051:157: sa la bkra shis 'byung ba lnga //
NK041(di)051:158: me chu sa rlung tshogs kyis bskor //
NK041(di)051:159: bar na bkra shis dkon mchog gsum //
NK041(di)051:160: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas tshogs kyis bskor //
NK041(di)051:161: dkon mchog gsum gyi bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:162: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:166: gnam sa bar gyi bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:167: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:168: dbus na bkra shis don gyi lha //
NK041(di)051:169: rnam par snang mdzad bkra shis don gyi lha //
NK041(di)051:170: rnam par snang mdzad bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:171: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:172: shar na bkra shis don gyi lha //
NK041(di)051:173: rdo rje sems dpa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:174: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:175: lho na bkra shis don gyi lha //
NK041(di)051:176: rin chen 'byung gnas bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:177: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:178: nub na bkra shis don gyi lha //
NK041(di)051:179: snang ba mtha' yas bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:180: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:181: byang na bkra shis don gyi lha //
NK041(di)051:182: don yod grub pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:183: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:189: bdag dang skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK041(di)051:190: deng gi rgyu sbyor yon gyi bdag /
NK041(di)051:191: sangs rgyas rnams kyis byin brlabs nas //
NK041(di)051:192: bkra shis dam pa'i mdo sde 'di //
NK041(di)051:193: nga yis brjod pa'i bsod nams kyis //
NK041(di)051:194: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab cing //
NK041(di)051:195: nyi zla lta bur kun gsal te //
NK041(di)051:196: skar tshogs lta bur grangs mang zhing //
NK041(di)051:197: sprin tshogs lta bur lhun grub ste //
NK041(di)051:198: 'ja' tshon lta bur mdzes sdug cing //
NK041(di)051:199: ri rab lta bur brtan brjid che //
NK041(di)051:200: sa gzhi lta bur kun bskyed cing //
NK041(di)051:201: rgya mtsho lta bur gting zab pa'i //
NK041(di)051:202: ljon shing lta bur 'dab rgyas te //
NK041(di)051:203: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen ltar //
NK041(di)051:204: dgos 'dod bkra shis char ltar 'bab gyur cig /
NK041(di)051:208: dmigs pa med pa sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin //
NK041(di)051:209: sbyin pa chen po'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:210: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:211: 'chal pa med pa tshul khrims pha rol phyin //
NK041(di)051:212: tshul khrims chen po'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:213: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:214: byung tshor med pa bzod pa'i pha rol phyin //
NK041(di)051:215: bzod pa chen po'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:216: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:217: le lo med pa brtson 'grus pha rol phyin //
NK041(di)051:218: brtson 'grus chen po'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:219: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:220: 'gyur ldog med pa bsam gtan pha rol phyin //
NK041(di)051:221: bsam gtan chen po'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:222: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:223: gang yang ma 'gags thabs kyi pha rol phyin //
NK041(di)051:224: thabs chen mchog gi bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:225: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:226: ma chags thogs med stobs kyi pha rol phyin //
NK041(di)051:227: stobs chen shugs kyi bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:228: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:229: re dogs med pa smon lam pha rol phyin //
NK041(di)051:230: smon lam chen po'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:231: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:232: 'khrul pa med pa shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK041(di)051:233: shes rab chen po'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:234: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:235: pha rol phyin bcu'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:236: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:237: bde legs thams cad myur thob shog /
NK041(di)051:242: p+aa ra sang+ga te bo d+hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)051:243: ma chags thogs med 'khor lo rin po che //
NK041(di)051:244: 'khor lo rin chen bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:245: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:246: theg chen stobs ldan glang po rin po che //
NK041(di)051:247: glang po rin chen bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:248: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:249: cang shes shugs ldan rta mchog rin po che //
NK041(di)051:250: rta mchog rin chen bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:251: bkra shis des kyang deg 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:252: kun la dbang sgyur blon po rin po che //
NK041(di)051:253: blon po rin chen bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:254: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:255: log rtog dpung 'joms dmag dpon rin po che //
NK041(di)051:256: dmag dpon rin chen bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:257: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:258: thams cad kun bskyed btsun mo rin po che //
NK041(di)051:259: btsun mo rin chen bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:260: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:261: de ma thag tu bdag cag bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:262: bsam 'phel don grub nor bu rin po che //
NK041(di)051:263: nor bu rin chen bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:264: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:267: sa ma mud ga ti se s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)051:268: bar+ya su le b+h+ra ma khram tse /
NK041(di)051:269: smra ra ts+tshe da n+aa ny+tshe s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)051:270: na mo dbu la bkra shis gdugs ltar skyob //
NK041(di)051:271: sku la bkra shis mi nub rgyal mtshan mchog /
NK041(di)051:272: gsung la bkra shis chos dung g.yas su 'khyil //
NK041(di)051:273: thugs la bkra shis dpal gyi be'u gsal //
NK041(di)051:274: spyan la bkra shis rin chen gser gyi nya //
NK041(di)051:275: ljags la bkra shis pad+mo lo 'dab rgyas //
NK041(di)051:276: mgul la bkra shis rin chen bum pa 'khyil //
NK041(di)051:277: phyag la bkra shis yon tan nor bu mchog /
NK041(di)051:278: zhabs la bkra shis 'phrin las 'khor lo lnga //
NK041(di)051:279: bkra shis rdzas brgyad dngos grub dam pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)051:280: rdzas mchog brgyad kyi bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK041(di)051:281: deng 'dir bdag cag rnams la bkra shis phob //
NK041(di)051:282: bkra shis des kyang rtag tu bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:283: sarba +aa yur+dz+ny+aana rata na ha mu ki /
NK041(di)051:287: sangs rgyas zhal nas gsungs pa yi //
NK041(di)051:288: bkra shis brtsegs pa'i smon lam mdo //
NK041(di)051:289: tshe 'dir bde skyid tshe ring zhing //
NK041(di)051:290: bkra shis dpal dang longs spyod thob //
NK041(di)051:291: bsod nams phun sum tshogs ldan 'thob //
NK041(di)051:292: phyi ma bla med rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK041(di)051:293: zhes bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa dang /
NK041(di)051:294: bkra shis dang ldan pa'i 'khor de dag dang /
NK041(di)051:295: lha dang mi dang lha ma yin du bcas pa
NK041(di)051:296: de dag bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la rjes
NK041(di)051:298: de bzhin gshegs pa la mngon par bstod do //
NK041(di)051:299: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das la 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas gsol ba /
NK041(di)051:300: bcom ldan 'das kyi mdo sde 'di'i ji ltar las cho ga dang ldan par bgyi /
NK041(di)051:301: de'i cho ga ni ji ltar bgyi zhes gsol ba dang /
NK041(di)051:302: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK041(di)051:303: 'jam dpal 'di'i cho ga ni dkon mchog gi pho brang bzheng ba dang /
NK041(di)051:305: gtsug lag khang bzheng ba dang /
NK041(di)051:310: glegs bam la rab gnas byed pa dang /
NK041(di)051:311: yul mkhar gang du rtsig pa dang /
NK041(di)051:312: khang khyim gsar pa 'bubs pa dang /
NK041(di)051:314: bag ma gtong len byed pa dang /
NK041(di)051:318: bkra mi shis pa dang ltas ngan pa dag zlog par byed pa /
NK041(di)051:319: sgyur bar byed pa 'di ni kha zas gtsang zhing ro bro bar byed pa'am /
NK041(di)051:320: nas 'bras til la sogs pa'i 'bru sna lnga'am /
NK041(di)051:324: 'brang rgyas lta bu la brjod par bya'o //
NK041(di)051:325: de'i phan yon ni bkra mi shis pa thams cad rab tu zhi nas /
NK041(di)051:326: tshe 'dir bkra shis kun ldan zhing //
NK041(di)051:327: bla med 'bras bu thob ces bka' stsal to //
NK041(di)051:328: sku yi bkra shis skye med chos kyi sku //
NK041(di)051:329: gsung gi bkra shis dam chos bdud rtsi'i sgra //
NK041(di)051:330: thugs kyi bkra shis mnyam nyid 'khrul pa med //
NK041(di)051:331: yon tan bkra shis 'gro drug gnas nas 'dren //
NK041(di)051:332: 'phrin las bkra shis rtsol med lhun gyis grub //
NK041(di)051:333: nyin yang bkra shis mtshan yang bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)051:334: nyin mtshan rtag tu bkra shis bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:335: rkang gnyis khyed cag bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:336: rkang bzhi khyed cag bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:337: da ltar byung rnams bde legs shog /
NK041(di)051:338: kun kyang bde skyid mchog thob shog /
NK041(di)051:339: skam ka ra skam ka ra nir gad tsa ta /
